This project is still in vigorous, active development, and will contain bugs which could damage your system. It aims to produce a fast installation of basic Arch Linux with Xfce desktop environment and LXDM greeter.

How to use it:

1) Requirements ... Running a live Arch session (as 'root') A working internet connection

2) Update package list and install git: pacman -Sy git

3) Get the script: git clone git://github.com/Angeltoast/Achoo

4) Run it: cd Achoo && ./achoo
